snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Official Ken, Blanka, Dhalsim, and E. Honda Reveal & Game Mode Trailer | TGS 2022
snippet.description:
Watch the latest Street Fighter 6 trailer revealing that Ken, Blanka, Dhalsim, and E. Honda have joined the roster for the upcoming fighting game. 

The new trailer also gives us our first detailed look at SF6's World Tour. Players will be able to fully customize their avatars and equip gear that suits their playstyle. Hit the streets with Luke as your guide and learn from the masters along the way. You can bring your avatar into the Battle Hub to play online matches, get stuck into tournaments, or play classic Capcom games. Additionally, we see Extreme Battle - a party mode where you can set up unusual rules and gimmicks for matches.

#IGN #Gaming #StreetFighter
